ntopng categorizes hosts using services are provided by http://block.si

In order to use these categorization services you need to mail info@block.si and
ask for a test key to be used in ntopng.

For test driving the service please use as key 9hoAtewwpC2tXRMJBfifrY24B
(example ntopng -c 9hoAtewwpC2tXRMJBfifrY24B .....).

If you want to disable categorization, please do "-c none"


NOTES:
- THIS IS AN EXPERIMENTAL SERVICE WE WILL FURTHER DEVELOP IN THE NEAR FUTURE
- NTOPNG WILL CONTACT DIRECTLY BLOCK.SI (NO TRAFFIC WILL PASS THROUGH NTOP.ORG)
